1.in dockerfile each and every command is a layer that gets bulild upon each
  other like a stack..where every time you build the docker image (an image is static container that is yet to be run)

2.Reason for why we first run COPY pacakage.json
  Reason for why we first run COPY pacakage.json before we actually COPY all the source code realted to our project is that 
  the chances for changing of our json file is very low so the docker software is smart enough to not download this file 
  again because there are no changes mode to this json file.
  ****Docker caches the each and every result

3.every command is the step by step building of our custom docker image file  

  